com.neosensory.tlepredictionengine

Class Sgp4

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.neosensory.tlepredictionengine.Sgp4

  • public class Sgp4
extends java.lang.Object
    This class provides sgp4 procedures for analytical propagation * of a satellite. the code was originally released in the 1980 and 1986 * spacetrack papers. a detailed discussion of the theory and history * may be found in the 2006 aiaa paper by vallado, crawford, hujsak, * and kelso.
